dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Louis Jones. May I have your name, please?
Nice to meet you, Crystal. How can I assist you today?
I need to report an incident. My vehicle was rear-ended yesterday.
I'm sorry to hear that, Crystal. Can you provide me with your policy number and the date of the incident?
My policy number is seven eight five six four three two and the incident occurred on zero four one zero two zero two.
Thank you for the information. We will start processing your claim. Is there anything else you need assistance with?
No, that's all for now. Thank you.
You're welcome, Crystal. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day.
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Goodbye.
